@baseUrl = http://localhost:4600/api
@jwt = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### ERP product search proxy
GET {{baseUrl}}/integrations/erp/products/search?ean=TSC480&branchId=02
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### ERP customer search proxy
GET {{baseUrl}}/integrations/erp/customers/search?q=garza&branchId=02&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### AI extraction from text proxy
POST {{baseUrl}}/integrations/ai/extraction/text
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Need 20 check valves 2 in, 80 m carbon steel pipe 4 in sch40",
  "source": "email"
}

### AI extraction from file proxy
POST {{baseUrl}}/integrations/ai/extraction/file
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=Boundary

--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="quote.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< /absolute/path/to/quote.pdf
--Boundary--
